{"tid":932160,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"肥芝們可唔可以入一入黎","createTime":"2018-12-07T13:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T14:34:38.000Z","uid":142304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"418432c6ee2256e0c98b088ab1489883db9a139c","tid":932160,"uid":142304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想問你地係咪真係覺得自己咁有魅力？<br />\n瘦到個個忍唔住望你？<br />\n個個都鐘意你？<br />\n你地嘅世界係咪所有生物望下你都代表對你一見鍾情？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尤其是係嗰啲鍾意搞小圈子嘅肥芝<br />\n好老實講<br />\n行過唔小心望到你<br />\n唔會係代表對你一見鍾情<br />\n可唔可以唔好再周圍同人講<br />\n「我好鍾意你」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我好撚憎你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到你哋對自己咁有自信嘅時候<br />\n可唔可以話我知你啲自信係邊度黎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:紅巴，俾個肥芝煩左成年<br />\n煩到我想追嗰個女仔真係以為我鍾意佢"},{"pid":"9ab9aad846f314458ea50e0ad846f7e174c2df70","tid":932160,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"abcea178e4b8c47c93b6bf32b284d0e7d6ebe874","tid":932160,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"有無煩右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}